This paper discusses the design challenges and solutions for IEEE 802.11ay-based mmWave WLANs, which involves topics related to networking (NI), information theory (IT), multimedia (MM), augmented reality (AR), and systems and control (SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI, followed by cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.AR, and cs.SY.
